===Verb V===
'''{{ARchar|[[تقطب]]}}''' (taqáʈʈaba)

# to become [[gloomy]] ''(countenance)''

===Verb X===
'''{{ARchar|[[استقطب]]}}''' (istáqʈaba)

# to [[polarize]]

